Permanently delete a draft. Use this when a recovered draft is no longer wanted instead of leaving it in the drafts list

Usage: mxr drafts discard <DRAFT_ID>

Arguments:
  <DRAFT_ID>  Draft ID to delete

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
